* [[Twisted Flipside]]: 0-cost; Manipulate; Set the coin; '''Expend'''.
* [[Boosted Set]]: 0-cost; Manipulate; Choose: Rig 2 '''Heads''' or 2 '''Snails'''; '''Expend'''.
